Privacy Policy for Drowzy

Effective Date: [Insert Date]

Drowzy is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how the app handles user data.

1. Information We Collect
   Drowzy does not collect, store, or share any personal data.

2. Camera Usage
   Drowzy uses your device’s camera solely for real-time drowsiness detection.
   No images or videos are recorded, stored, or transmitted. All processing happens locally on your device.

3. Data Storage
   Drowzy may store basic trip statistics (such as duration and alert counts) locally on your device. This data is not shared externally.

4. Third-Party Services
   Drowzy uses on-device machine learning tools. No user data is sent to external servers.

5. Security
   Since no personal data is collected or transmitted, your information remains secure on your device.

6. Changes to This Policy
   We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected within the app or on the hosting page.

7. Contact
